quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  70,36,"E ko heɓi yedduɓe ɓen takko maaɗa, hiɓe heñora"
  70,37,"ka nano e ka ñaamo, ko ɓe dentoy-dentoy"
  70,38,Hara gooto kala e maɓɓe tamƴinoto naatoygol Aljanna neemaaji
  70,39,Ɗun waɗataa ! Men tagiriɓe ko ɓe anndi
  70,40,"Mi woondirii Jeyɗo fuɗirɗe e mutirɗe On, pellet, ko Men hattanɓe"
  70,41,"wattitirgol ɓe ko ɓuri ɓe moƴƴude, Men siforaa ronkugol [ɗum]"
  70,42,"Accuɓe ɓe jumpa, ɓe fija haa ɓe hawroya e ñalaande maɓɓe nde ɓe kammbirananoo"
  70,43,"ñalnde ɓe yaltiroyta e genaale ɗen heñaare, wa si tawii ko kaaƴe (sanamu) ɓe woni wugganaade"
  70,44,"Hara gite maɓɓe no heli, koyeera no suddi ɓe. Ko nden ñalaande woni ko ɓe kammbirananoo"